    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过《荷鲁斯：沙漠生存者》步入古埃及的神话世界。这是一款令人兴奋的融合之作，将类生存动作游戏和牌组构建策略游戏有机结合在一起。扮演荷鲁斯的角色，对战腐化的神明、神话般的野兽以及无穷无尽的敌群，并在此过程中实现复仇以及为父辈之地恢复平衡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269340/extras/b2ff01599f7fc88748e43045879ceca8.poster.avif?t=1770450727\" width=600 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269340/extras/b2ff01599f7fc88748e43045879ceca8.webm?t=1770450727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269340/extras/b2ff01599f7fc88748e43045879ceca8.mp4?t=1770450727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对持续袭来的敌人浪潮，从腐化的神祗到神话般的生物。掌握战斗技能并释放神性力量，从而净化堕落者并力挽狂澜。随着敌群在每次遭遇战中变得更强，努力适应各种各样的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269340/extras/dda062451fe23bfd3dcd208240f6b2e0.poster.avif?t=1770450727\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269340/extras/dda062451fe23bfd3dcd208240f6b2e0.webm?t=1770450727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269340/extras/dda062451fe23bfd3dcd208240f6b2e0.mp4?t=1770450727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过讲求策略的牌组构建来打造你的魔法武器军械库。糅合神性法器、古代武器和训练，从而创造能够在战斗中给予你优势的协同作用。每一个选择都会塑造你的旅程，并强化你的生存能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269340/extras/eb8ac979760a081211cf1f2557d9b75e.poster.avif?t=1770450727\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269340/extras/eb8ac979760a081211cf1f2557d9b75e.webm?t=1770450727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269340/extras/eb8ac979760a081211cf1f2557d9b75e.mp4?t=1770450727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在穿梭于远古神庙、受诅咒之地和无情沙漠的过程中，逐步锻造你的使命。做出影响深远的选择，它们会定义你的游玩方式、解锁新的能力并决定你的终极命运。你是会屈服于腐化，还是会将其踩在脚下实现升华？</p>",
